        "review_1": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": "4.9",
            "quote": "\"I forgot what normal felt like until now!\"",
            "details": "I got so used to the dryness I honestly forgot it wasn't supposed to feel like that?? Like I just accepted it as my life. Started Huuha Queen because my cousin wouldn't stop talking about it and within like 2 weeks I actually felt wet again on my own. Not from lube. From my actual body. I didn't even realize how uncomfortable I had been every single day until it stopped. I literally feel normal again and I could cry!!",
            "author_name": "TIFFANY W.",
            "author_image": "shopify://shop_images/dts11.png",
            "tag_1": "Immunity Boost",
            "tag_2": "Prevention",
            "card_bg_color": ""
          }
        },
        "review_2": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": "5.0",
            "quote": "\"Husband noticed before I even said anything!\"",
            "details": "Ok I need to share this because WOW. We been together 14 years and I'm not gonna lie there was a point where we just stopped being close. I was dry and self conscious and I didn't want him near me like that. He never said anything but I know he felt it too. Started taking Huuha Queen and didn't tell him. About 3 weeks in he looks at me and goes \"something's different about you.\" He had no idea I was taking anything!! We are all over each other again like it's year one. This is my little secret and it's WORKING 🤫",
            "author_name": "BRANDI M.",
            "author_image": "shopify://shop_images/dts10.png",
            "tag_1": "Gut Support",
            "tag_2": "Bloat Relief",
            "card_bg_color": ""
          }
        },
        "review_3": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": "4.9",
            "quote": "\"I stopped carrying wipes everywhere I go!\"",
            "details": "I'm not even exaggerating when I say I used to have wipes in my purse, my car, my desk at work, everywhere. I would go to the bathroom before any meeting just to check. I was changing my underwear sometimes twice a day because of the smell and discharge and I was SO embarrassed even though nobody knew. After about 2 weeks on Huuha Queen the odor just started fading. By the end of the first bag I realized I hadn't checked once that whole day!! The freshness is actually real. I feel clean like when I was younger. I tell everyone about these now.",
            "author_name": "CANDICE R.",
            "author_image": "shopify://shop_images/dts5.png",
            "tag_1": "Clean Ingredients",
            "tag_2": "Whole-Body Health",
            "card_bg_color": ""
          }
        },
        "review_4": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": "5.0",
            "quote": "\"I'm 58 and thought this was just my life now!\"",
            "details": "I honestly thought the dryness was just permanent. My doctor said try lubricant and that was literally her whole answer. I tried so many different creams and lubes I have a whole basket of them in my bathroom and NONE of them lasted or felt right. My daughter found Huuha Queen online and sent it to me. I didn't expect anything. By the third week everything started feeling alive again not just during intimacy but even just sitting and walking around all day! I almost cried because I forgot what it felt like to just be comfortable in my own body. Thank you Huuha Queen for real!!!",
            "author_name": "JASMINE L.",
            "author_image": "shopify://shop_images/dts6.png",
            "tag_1": "Cold Prevention",
            "tag_2": "Daily Defense",
            "card_bg_color": ""
          }
        },
        "review_5": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": "4.8",
            "quote": "\"Finally, a supplement I can actually feel working.\"",
            "details": "I've tried so many supplements that promise results but never deliver. Huuha Queen is different. Within the first week I noticed more energy and less bloating. I'm a customer for life.",
