    "collapsible_content_TCEeNz": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_row_kP7dka": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do the Huuha Queen™ Slippery Huuha gummies work?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Huuha Queen uses three ingredients that work from the inside out. <strong>Slippery Elm</strong> rehydrates the tissue that produces your natural moisture. <strong>Bacillus Coagulans</strong> is a probiotic that survives stomach acid to actually reach your vaginal flora and rebalance pH. <strong>Pineapple Fruit</strong> supports freshness naturally. Two gummies a day — your body does the rest.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_jgAFHc": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long will it take to see results?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Most women notice changes <strong>within the first 2 weeks</strong>, with full results building over <strong>30 days</strong> of daily use. Take 2 gummies daily. Every body is different — some feel it in the first week, others take 3-4 weeks. Stick with it. The women who see the best results are the ones who stay consistent.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_qUEDkw": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I take it with other supplements?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes. These gummies are made with <strong>natural ingredients and work alongside your other daily vitamins</strong>. If you're currently on specific medications or hormonal treatments, check with your doctor first.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_FCYENr": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is this safe if I can't use estrogen or hormones?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes. Huuha Queen is <strong>100% hormone-free and contains zero estrogen</strong>. It works naturally with your body — no hormones at all. Women on aromatase inhibitors, women who've been through cancer treatment, and women who simply don't want hormones can use this safely.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_JXE9KX": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Are they vegan and gluten-free?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes. Made with <strong>vegan, gluten-free, allergen-free, non-GMO, and natural ingredients</strong> — safe for a wide range of dietary needs.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_xwHJdL": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Are there any side effects?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>These gummies work with your body's own system, not against it. Our probiotic strain is <strong>stomach-friendly and won't disrupt your natural balance</strong>. No hormones, no harsh chemicals, no digestive issues. Most women experience zero side effects. Take 2 gummies daily with food.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
